title: Would you like -BaBaYeit- to become a multisig signer?
body:
Hey Yeti Clan!
I'm throwing my hat in the ring to become apart of the multisig signers, and I can only do that with your support.

I've recently gotten super invested into tokenomics, and I feel this would be a great space to not only give forth effort and ideas for the community, but also learn and grow as an individual in this ecosystem. I promise to dox myself to the T to ensure nothing is blind from the public eye of the community.

The time is now my fellow Yetis!
the best of wishes,
BaBaYeit
